        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Fair COLA for Seniors Act of 2023</strong></p> <p>This bill bases cost-of-living adjustments for certain benefits available through federal and military retirement programs, Social Security, and specified programs for veterans on a price index that tracks the spending patterns of older consumers. The Bureau of Labor Statistics of the Department of Labor must publish that price index on a monthly basis.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
